list.abstract: money（英[ˈmʌni]，美[ˈmʌni]），英语单词，名词，意思为货币；钱；金钱。短语搭配有save money（省钱；节约金钱；节省金钱），例句为“Cutting out paper towels would save trees (树), water, air and our money.（减少纸巾将节省树木、水、空气和我们的钱。）” money名词类近义词有currency、wealth、treasure等。
《Money》是迈克尔·约瑟夫·杰克逊作词、作曲并演唱的一首歌曲，收录于迈克尔·约瑟夫·杰克逊1995年6月20日发行的专辑《HIStory: Past, Present and Future, Book I》中。

yingyinNormal.en: In terms of money, we have no money.
yingyinNormal.zh: 关于投资我们没钱了

yingyinNormal.en: I don't need the money.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不需要钱。

yingyinNormal.en: They've got money, right? I don't want their money!
yingyinNormal.zh: 他们有钱，对吧？但我不想要他们的钱。

yingyinNormal.en: You talked about the money?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你还提到了那笔钱？

yingyinNormal.en: Every mobster needs a money guy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 黑帮也需要人管钱。

yingyinNormal.en: The money's not with him, Mark.
yingyinNormal.zh: 钱不在他那儿，马克。

yingyinNormal.en: What happened to all of our money?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们的钱跑哪去了呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Wow, you got a lot of money in there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你这儿有很多钱啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey. Rach, did you make your money?
yingyinNormal.zh: 嘿，瑞秋，钱拿到没有？

yingyinNormal.en: There's nothing I can do with this money.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我无法使用这笔钱。

yingyinNormal.en: No, I can't. Don't you need money?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不能要。你不是需要钱么？

yingyinNormal.en: Please tell me we're playing for money.
yingyinNormal.zh: 快告诉我咱们是玩钱的。

yingyinNormal.en: Yes. We got more money than Davy Crockett.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对，我们挣了一大堆钱。

yingyinNormal.en: No need. It was money well spent. Why?
yingyinNormal.zh: 不必，这钱花的值。什么意思？

yingyinNormal.en: Your fingerprints are all over this money.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这笔钱上到处是你的痕迹。

yingyinNormal.en: But. Don't you have to give him his money back?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不是应该把钱还给他？

yingyinNormal.en: If you want, I could loan you some money.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果你有需要，我可以借你一些钱

yingyinNormal.en: Sounds like the kind of money I'm familiar with.
yingyinNormal.zh: 感觉是我很熟悉的一种钱。

yingyinNormal.en: Now take this money and get the hell outta here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在拿上这些钱，快滚吧。

yingyinNormal.en: So, you stole my joke, and you stole my money.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你偷我的笑话，还偷我的钱。
